---
import RegisterButton from './RegisterButton.astro';
---
<section class="section section--muted">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about">
      <img src="/images/marlon-marescia-microsoft.jpg" alt="Marlon Marescia" width="620" height="604" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
      <div>
        <h2 style="margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);">Hosted by Marlon Marescia</h2>
        <p>
          For <strong>over 15 years</strong> Marlon has run paid advertising and lead-generation campaigns
          in some of the most competitive industries in Australia - and trained others to do the same.
        </p>
        <p>
          Today he <strong>teaches businesses internationally</strong> how to use Facebook Ads
          to win more clients, and he owns multiple marketing agencies - including
          <strong>The Sales Driven Website</strong>, <strong>Voyager Agency</strong>, and
          <strong>Kenkoo</strong>.
        </p>
        <p>
          What separates Marlon from a typical marketer - and what makes this webinar different - is what
          he measures. <strong>He doesn't care about clicks, likes, or shares. He cares about one number:
          the sale.</strong> In a private school, that's the enrolment. Every campaign he builds, every
          dollar of ad spend, every minute of a parent's attention - it all has to ladder up to enrolled
          students, or it doesn't count.
        </p>
        <p>
          This webinar brings that same business-world method - <em>measured by enrolments, not
          impressions</em> - into the private school sector for the first time.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: var(--space-lg);">
          <RegisterButton label="Register for the Webinar" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
